TITLETEXT: BulpTempCalc Warning
GADGETSTEXT: _OK
IMAGE: 2
BODYTEXT:  Your health is at risk.
BODYTEXT: 
BODYTEXT:  If the wet-bulb temperature reaches 35°C or above, there is an
BODYTEXT:  acute risk to life within 6 hours at the latest!!
BODYTEXT: 
BODYTEXT:  Higher temperatures will shorten this time frame.
INVISIBLE: 0
MAXCHARS: 10
